PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology of certain persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Federal Business Development Bank to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (ELIZABETH ANN CARMICHAEL, Glace Bay, Nova Scotia, in the place of Robert E. Stafford, whose term has expired; DOREEN BRAVERMAN, Vancouver, British Columbia, in the place of Bill Tsakumis, whose term has expired; and RITA DE SANTIS, Montreal, Quebec, in the place of Rinaldo Canonico, whose term has expired)
